#

Lazy Borscht

45 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

SoupQuick MealHearty

Description

A quick and hearty beet soup with a touch of cream, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 cups, shredded
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrot: 1, grated
  • potato: 1, diced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
